{"tid":437353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"離家失去音訊 沙田男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-10-16T02:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T11:21:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46292ae67aa92fd01756c2bda0f2b3aa98c959ab","tid":437353,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n沙田插桅杆街欣庭軒5座，早上6時許，一名男子離開住所後，從大廈高處墮下重創，倒卧在行人路邊草地上，昏迷不醒，稍後，其妻發現丈夫失蹤，四出找尋，約半小時後，揭發丈夫昏迷在草地上，於是報警，救護員到場，證實男子已經死亡，警員封鎖現場，及聯絡死者妻子展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57337207&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57337207%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171016&d=oakFjxmgHF0hgzt0QCe%2FCywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=942db389\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57337207%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171016&h=920d3f63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57337207&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171016</a>"},{"pid":"1652952ce906190533ff787827fbbd898c9be0a9","tid":437353,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b8948d822c455d783716a9374a7ad14132c8ed","tid":437353,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"